Tarreos, giggles, phone calls
You're into your job, but you're abruptly getting rid of your colleagues' giggles?
Have you inadvertently heard a telephone conversation that would have been better not to listen to it?
Don't bother your colleagues with your tarareos, chants, conversations out loud (less when you do them above their head), kicking, constant blasphemies, expressing your discontents out loud.
